nnitrogen and hydrogen could be present in the ionosphere of Titan. Here, we\nidentified some protonated ions, which are reactive species that could\nparticipate to the erosion of organic aerosols on Titan.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 3 Mar 2023 12:25:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-03"}
